        Template:
        <suppress>
            <notes>CVE-YYYY-XXXXX: [reason this does not apply / compensating control].
                   Reviewed: YYYY-MM-DD. Re-review by: YYYY-MM-DD.</notes>
            <cve>CVE-YYYY-XXXXX</cve>
        </suppress>
    -->
</suppressions>
